This hybrid comes from ogre and human parents. They average 7 to 8 feet 
tall, have ruddy complexions, dark hair, and dark eyes. They look much
like huge humans.

Due to their huge size, half-ogres have a +1 to their initial Strength and
Constitution scores, and a -1 to their Charisa score. They also inherit 
the dull wit of their ogre parent, suffer a -1 to Intelligence.